    .docs-content
      h1 Floating Action Button Vue Component
      p Floating action buttons are used for a promoted action. They are distinguished by a circled icon floating above the UI and have motion behaviors that include morphing, launching, and a transferring anchor point.
      p Floating Action Button Vue component represents <a href="../docs/floating-action-button.html">Floating Action Button</a> element.
      h2 Usage examples
      h4 Floating action button
      pre
        code
          :code
            <f7-fab color="pink" @click="doSomething">
              <f7-icon icon="icon-plus"></f7-icon>
            </f7-fab>
      p Renders to:
      pre
        code
          :code
            <a href="#" class="floating-action-button color-pink">
              <i class="icon icon-plus"></i>
            </a>
      h4 Speed Dial
      pre
        code
          :code
            <f7-fab-speed-dial>
              <!-- Actions -->
              <f7-fab-actions>
                <f7-fab-action color="pink" @click="onActionClick">A</f7-fab-action>
                <f7-fab-action color="orange" @click="onActionClick">B</f7-fab-action>
                <f7-fab-action color="green" @click="onActionClick">C</f7-fab-action>
              </f7-fab-actions>
              <!-- FAB -->
              <f7-fab>
                <!-- First icon to open Actions -->
                <f7-icon icon="icon-plus"></f7-icon>
                <!-- Second icon to close Actions -->
                <f7-icon icon="icon-close"></f7-icon>
              </f7-fab>
            </f7-fab-speed-dial>
      p Renders to:
      pre
        code
          :code
            <div class="speed-dial">
              <!-- Actions -->
              <div class="speed-dial-buttons">
                <a href="#" class="pink">A</a>
                <a href="#" class="orange">B</a>
                <a href="#" class="green">C</a>
              </div>
              <!-- FAB -->
              <a href="#" class="floating-action-button color-pink">
                <i class="icon icon-plus"></i>
                <i class="icon icon-close"></i>
              </a>
            </div>
